            "creation_date": 1384944541,
            "body": "<p>You can just used an old fashioned <code>for<\/code> loop instead of an enhanced <code>for<\/code> loop:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Arrays.sort(distances);// sorts array from highest to lowest        \nfor (int i = 0; i &lt; distances.lengh; ++i) {\n    System.out.println(\"index: \" + i + \":[\" + val + \"],\");\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
